{"tid":1886872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要《榮光歲月》嘅手足，最後機會！","createTime":"2020-02-19T07:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:55:45.000Z","uid":107053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc09d59422d05021562c08a18b61d3646abc65b","tid":1886872,"uid":107053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"《榮光歲月》會於明日（2月20日）最後加推，要嘅手足就快手！<br />\n<br />\n【最新消息】<br />\n感謝支持！《榮光歲月》上月甫推出即被搶購一空，現決定於本周四（2月20日）最後加推，香港人，加油！<br />\n堪輿學有種現象叫「逢九必災」，2019年的災難，由人禍引起，始作俑者是一名自稱受到上帝感召而參選行政長官的天主教徒。這位黨國使徒假借「彰顯公義」之名，發動送中法，撼動一國兩制，挑起九七以來最嚴重的中港矛盾。她隻手燃點了由上水到西環的街頭怒火，引爆了由維園瀰漫到天水圍的毒氣彈，一發不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n災難是，戴口罩上街會犯法，警察裝扮成暴徒突襲市民，黑社會無差別毆打途人後會獲得警方拍膊頭放生；災難是，教師社工記者急救員履行天職會被懲罰，大學中學捍衞自由會被狙擊，空姐機師地勤守護天空會被辭職。<br />\n<br />\n寧投熊熊烈火，不伴寂寂朽木。在艱險的抗爭路上，香港人奮起頑抗。當毒氣圍城水炮橫飛，我們戴上口罩繼續上街；當白衣人與Green object恐襲平民，我們昂首拒默沉和你拖和你lunch。當政權禮崩樂壞信望墮入深淵，民間的文明已進化昇華至新的高度。<br />\n<br />\n置身風火彈雨當中，《蘋果》記者老是常出現在警盾之前、催淚煙之間，用鏡頭見證歷史的血和淚，用紙筆記載時代的黑暗與輝煌。<br />\n<br />\n不知道這場反暴政運動會否延續至2047，只知道2019的炎夏怒火與凜冬烈燄，在五大訴求未遂前不會熄滅。《蘋果》謹在這歷史關口作個小結，以圖像和文字重新展現一場未完運動的跌宕成敗；我們輯錄了約500張新聞照片，找來運動不同參與者撰文自白，與香港人一同回首挽手走過的榮光歲月。<br />\n<br />\n《榮光歲月》每本200元，2月20日起再在全港報攤、7-11及OK便利店發售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200219/Y6XESUWPNER2IS4UD4Z6AUFUTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200219%2FY6XESUWPNER2IS4UD4Z6AUFUTU%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=67c62703\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200219%2FY6XESUWPNER2IS4UD4Z6AUFUTU%2F&h=7cd98241\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200219/Y6XESUWPNER2IS4UD4Z6AUFUTU/</a>"},{"pid":"064069b41bdb6a4e6191ae3b186f67185c7c714b","tid":1886872,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.defiance-voices-hk.com/home-ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defiance-voices-hk.com%2Fhome-ch&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=511fb57a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.defiance-voices-hk.com/home-ch</a><br />\n之前買唔到榮光訂咗依2本，依家仲買唔買埋榮光好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2dd518876d1ea4107366e71a3de7565cda8eb2","tid":1886872,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:33:20.000Z","msg":"中環D報紙檔根本日日都見到有"},{"pid":"3acaa4c963d6c081a17eb24c837db1e144e543c9","tid":1886872,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:16:43.000Z","msg":"搵唔到"},{"pid":"02fbb674e91add00dcd641b2f8a9c166c7ec884e","tid":1886872,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"油麻地有"},{"pid":"a72638e61b7145ff221588dfe85b5481e65f35d6","tid":1886872,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"終於買撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444009e8bdbd15f446c35f8653680038794b704e","tid":1886872,"uid":71629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"064069b41bdb6a4e6191ae3b186f67185c7c714b","tid":1886872,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.defiance-voices-hk.com/home-ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defiance-voices-hk.com%2Fhome-ch&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=511fb57a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.defiance-voices-hk.com/home-ch</a><br />\n之前買唔到榮光訂咗依2本，依家仲買唔買埋榮光好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"買，一睇相同內文，你就知道係值得"},{"pid":"810bd83df92034f8d652acf2e9f8951068aa516e","tid":1886872,"uid":106528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:55:45.000Z",